89static inline ResourceRequest constructRevalidationRequest(const Key& key, const SubresourceInfo& subResourceInfo, const Entry* entry)
90{
91 ResourceRequest revalidationRequest(key.identifier());
92 revalidationRequest.setHTTPHeaderFields(subResourceInfo.requestHeaders());
93 revalidationRequest.setFirstPartyForCookies(subResourceInfo.firstPartyForCookies());
94 revalidationRequest.setIsSameSite(subResourceInfo.isSameSite());
95 revalidationRequest.setIsTopSite(subResourceInfo.isTopSite());
96 revalidationRequest.setIsAppBound(subResourceInfo.isAppBound());
97
98 if (!key.partition().isEmpty())
99 revalidationRequest.setCachePartition(key.partition());
100 ASSERT_WITH_MESSAGE(key.range().isEmpty(), "range is not supported");
101
102 revalidationRequest.makeUnconditional();
103 if (entry) {
104 String eTag = entry->response().httpHeaderField(HTTPHeaderName::ETag);
105 if (!eTag.isEmpty())
106 revalidationRequest.setHTTPHeaderField(HTTPHeaderName::IfNoneMatch, eTag);
107
108 String lastModified = entry->response().httpHeaderField(HTTPHeaderName::LastModified);
109 if (!lastModified.isEmpty())
110 revalidationRequest.setHTTPHeaderField(HTTPHeaderName::IfModifiedSince, lastModified);
111 }
112
113 revalidationRequest.setPriority(subResourceInfo.priority());
114
115 return revalidationRequest;
116}

293 return false;
294 }

297 logSpeculativeLoadingDiagnosticMessage(m_cache.networkProcess(), frameID, preloadedEntry->wasRevalidated() ? DiagnosticLoggingKeys::successfulSpeculativeWarmupWithRevalidationKey() : DiagnosticLoggingKeys::successfulSpeculativeWarmupWithoutRevalidationKey());

299 }
300
301 // Check pending speculative revalidations.
302 auto* pendingPreload = m_pendingPreloads.get(storageKey);

306 else
307 logSpeculativeLoadingDiagnosticMessage(m_cache.networkProcess(), frameID, DiagnosticLoggingKeys::unknownEntryRequestKey());

310 }
311

313 LOG(NetworkCacheSpeculativePreloading, "(NetworkProcess) Retrieval: revalidation already in progress for '%s' but unusable due to HTTP headers mismatch:", storageKey.identifier().utf8().data());

315 return false;
316 }
317
318 LOG(NetworkCacheSpeculativePreloading, "(NetworkProcess) Retrieval: revalidation already in progress for '%s':", storageKey.identifier().utf8().data());
319
320 return true;

348void SpeculativeLoadManager::registerLoad(const GlobalFrameID& frameID, const ResourceRequest& request, const Key& resourceKey, std::optional<NavigatingToAppBoundDomain> isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain)
349{
350 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
351 ASSERT(request.url().protocolIsInHTTPFamily());
352
353 if (!shouldRegisterLoad(request))
354 return;
355
356 auto isMainResource = request.requester() == ResourceRequest::Requester::Main;
357 if (isMainResource) {
358 // Mark previous load in this frame as completed if necessary.
359 if (auto* pendingFrameLoad = m_pendingFrameLoads.get(frameID))
360 pendingFrameLoad->markLoadAsCompleted();
361
362 ASSERT(!m_pendingFrameLoads.contains(frameID));
363
364 // Start tracking loads in this frame.
365 auto pendingFrameLoad = PendingFrameLoad::create(m_storage, resourceKey, [this, frameID] {
366 bool wasRemoved = m_pendingFrameLoads.remove(frameID);
367 ASSERT_UNUSED(wasRemoved, wasRemoved);
368 });
369 m_pendingFrameLoads.add(frameID, pendingFrameLoad.copyRef());
370
371 // Retrieve the subresources entry if it exists to start speculative revalidation and to update it.
372 retrieveSubresourcesEntry(resourceKey, [this, weakThis = makeWeakPtr(*this), frameID, pendingFrameLoad = WTFMove(pendingFrameLoad), requestIsAppBound = request.isAppBound(), isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain](std::unique_ptr<SubresourcesEntry> entry) {
373 if (!weakThis)
374 return;
375
376 if (entry)
377 startSpeculativeRevalidation(frameID, *entry, requestIsAppBound, isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain);
378
379 pendingFrameLoad->setExistingSubresourcesEntry(WTFMove(entry));
380 });
381 return;
382 }
383
384 if (auto* pendingFrameLoad = m_pendingFrameLoads.get(frameID))
385 pendingFrameLoad->registerSubresourceLoad(request, resourceKey);

480void SpeculativeLoadManager::revalidateSubresource(const SubresourceInfo& subresourceInfo, std::unique_ptr<Entry> entry, const GlobalFrameID& frameID, std::optional<NavigatingToAppBoundDomain> isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain)
481{
482 ASSERT(!entry || entry->needsValidation());
483
484 auto& key = subresourceInfo.key();
485
486 // Range is not supported.
487 if (!key.range().isEmpty())
488 return;
489
490 auto* pendingLoad = m_pendingFrameLoads.get(frameID);
491
492 // Delay first-party speculative loads until we've received the response for the main resource, in case the main resource
493 // response sets cookies that are needed for subsequent loads.
494 if (pendingLoad && !pendingLoad->didReceiveMainResourceResponse() && subresourceInfo.isFirstParty()) {
495 preconnectForSubresource(subresourceInfo, entry.get(), frameID, isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain);
496 pendingLoad->addPostMainResourceResponseTask([this, subresourceInfo, entry = WTFMove(entry), frameID, isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain]() mutable {
497 if (m_pendingPreloads.contains(subresourceInfo.key()))
498 return;
499
500 revalidateSubresource(subresourceInfo, WTFMove(entry), frameID, isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain);
501 });
502 return;
503 }
504
505 ResourceRequest revalidationRequest = constructRevalidationRequest(key, subresourceInfo, entry.get());
506
507 LOG(NetworkCacheSpeculativePreloading, "(NetworkProcess) Speculatively revalidating '%s':", key.identifier().utf8().data());
508
509 auto revalidator = makeUnique<SpeculativeLoad>(m_cache, frameID, revalidationRequest, WTFMove(entry), isNavigatingToAppBoundDomain, [this, key, revalidationRequest, frameID](std::unique_ptr<Entry> revalidatedEntry) {
510 ASSERT(!revalidatedEntry || !revalidatedEntry->needsValidation());
511 ASSERT(!revalidatedEntry || revalidatedEntry->key() == key);
512
513 auto protectRevalidator = m_pendingPreloads.take(key);
514 LOG(NetworkCacheSpeculativePreloading, "(NetworkProcess) Speculative revalidation completed for '%s':", key.identifier().utf8().data());
515
516 if (satisfyPendingRequests(key, revalidatedEntry.get())) {
517 if (revalidatedEntry)
518 logSpeculativeLoadingDiagnosticMessage(m_cache.networkProcess(), frameID, DiagnosticLoggingKeys::successfulSpeculativeWarmupWithRevalidationKey());
519 return;
520 }
521
522 if (revalidatedEntry)
523 addPreloadedEntry(WTFMove(revalidatedEntry), frameID, revalidationRequest);
524 });
525 m_pendingPreloads.add(key, WTFMove(revalidator));
526}

528static bool canRevalidate(const SubresourceInfo& subresourceInfo, const Entry* entry)
529{
530 ASSERT(!subresourceInfo.isTransient());
531 ASSERT(!entry || entry->needsValidation());
532
533 if (entry && entry->response().hasCacheValidatorFields())
534 return true;
535
536 auto seenAge = subresourceInfo.lastSeen() - subresourceInfo.firstSeen();
537 if (seenAge == 0_ms) {
538 LOG(NetworkCacheSpeculativePreloading, "Speculative load: Seen only once");
539 return false;
540 }
541
542 auto now = WallTime::now();
543 auto firstSeenAge = now - subresourceInfo.firstSeen();
544 auto lastSeenAge = now - subresourceInfo.lastSeen();
545 // Sanity check.
546 if (seenAge <= 0_ms || firstSeenAge <= 0_ms || lastSeenAge <= 0_ms)
547 return false;
548
549 // Load full resources speculatively if they seem to stay the same.
550 const auto minimumAgeRatioToLoad = 2. / 3;
551 const auto recentMinimumAgeRatioToLoad = 1. / 3;
552 const auto recentThreshold = 5_min;
553
554 auto ageRatio = seenAge / firstSeenAge;
555 auto minimumAgeRatio = lastSeenAge > recentThreshold ? minimumAgeRatioToLoad : recentMinimumAgeRatioToLoad;
556
557 LOG(NetworkCacheSpeculativePreloading, "Speculative load: ok=%d ageRatio=%f entry=%d", ageRatio > minimumAgeRatio, ageRatio, !!entry);
558
559 if (ageRatio > minimumAgeRatio)
560 return true;
561
562 return false;
563}
